description.narrative:
The overall objective of the project is to assist Serbia in achieving an inclusive democracy, with authorities at all levels acting in compliance with human dimension commitments and gender equality priorities.  There are two project objectives:  1) To further enhance the principles of good governance within the armed forces and  2) To consolidate the democratic character of civilian-military relations in Serbia, including the integration of gender perspective.
These objectives will be addressed through four sets of activities/result areas:
Result 1: Parliament performs oversight of the armed forces in a more efficient and effective manner;
Result 2: Good governance in the security sector is further promoted;
Result 3: Participation of civil society in democratization of the security sector is further strengthened;
Result 4: Education and expertise in the security sector are further advanced.
